 external electric field and the polarization induced\nby the field, which yields the magnetoelectric coupling, is reported. The\nresults show the possibility to control multiferroicity, including the FM and\nAFM phases, with help of an electric field application.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 28 Jul 2013 21:06:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-30"}
