 Green's functions and in impurity solver part\nof DMFT procedure is discussed and its extention to other models is also\npointed out.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Jul 2013 11:19:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 May 2014 05:58:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2015 08:35:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-24"}
